Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To rescue his brother Ace who \Nhas been captured by the navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy stowed away on a navy ship with \Nthe Pirate Empress Boa Hancock's help
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and headed to the Great \NPrison - Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the rest \Nof the Straw Hats
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had been sent to separate \Nislands by Bartholomew Kuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As time ticks down for the \Npublic execution of Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tensions at Navy \NHeadquarters are rising
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and preparations for \Nwar are underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made the \Nking of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Deadly Infiltration! The \NUnderwater Prison Impel Down!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you and Luffy to \Nbecome good marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead, both of you brothers \Nhave become notorious hoodlums.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you \Nheard about Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He picked a fight with the World \NGovernment at Water Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and destroyed the Judgement \NIsland - Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rushed there and gave him \Nsome tough-love with this fist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he didn't \Nlearn even a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he went and made a big \Nmess at Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of \Nmy grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. I told Luffy \Nabout his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A father? Do I have a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's name is \NMonkey D. Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a revolutionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was surprised to \Nknow about his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter to us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Luffy and \NI unfortunately
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have the blood of the world's most \Ninfamous criminals in our veins anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no way for \Nus to become marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took over the name "Portgaz" from \Nmy mother to whom I owe so much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never wanted to have my \Ngood-for-nothing father's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have any memory of \Nhim and I don't owe anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah yeah, I understand \Nbut he tried...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too valuable \Nto let die now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run as wild as you want \Non the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my son from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Momonga! \NI see a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose ship is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mark... I've \Nseen it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't remember, they \Nmust not be a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them go! There is no \Ntime to waste on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Look over there! \NIt's a big Sea King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he targets us, he can eat \Nthis whole ship with one bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't notice us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We came all this way but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is nothing \Nwe can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do \Nnow, Sister Alvida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you guys who \Nwanted to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and who spent a fortune \Non an Eternal Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because we really wanted to save Captain \NBuggy who has been taken to Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to enter the Calm Belt \Nwhere monsters have their nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think this ship \Ncan sail there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is only one other course \Nand that's exclusively for the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna open the \NGate of Justice for a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! We can't \Neven get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, Captain \NBuggy will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Along with his \Nfriend Ace-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! Look at how sad he is \Nthinking about the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impel Down is the greatest \Nprison in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's impossible to \Nbreak in or break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy the Clown's luck \Nas a pirate has run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the way \NCaptain Buggy will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Until the day he finds \NCaptain John's treasure island
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which he has been searching \Nfor with all his heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna stand \Nby Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a compassionate \Nlion you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this Big Top so \Nyou guys take a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! This is \NCaptain Buggy's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Buggy is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to march \Nup to death's doorstep -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I won't let you \Nwaste this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can chase after \NBuggy to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never stop \Nfollowing our Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's to the great \Nprison or the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that you're gonna \Ndie before you even see Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy! Thank \Nyou for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't forget what \Nyou've done for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a peaceful \Nexecution! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel your grief, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Momonga, \Nmarine code G100660.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to sail on the current \Nso prepare to open the Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy ship that Luffy \Nand Hancock are on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is approaching \Nthe Tub Current
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is exclusively \Nused by the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and connects three of the \Ngovernment's central facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:35.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,500)}"The Great Underwater Prison\NImpel Down"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, new guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you're eating without first \Npaying respect to our cell leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I say hello every \Ntime I eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rule that a newcomer \Nshould give his food to the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will learn ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait a minute! That \Nwas just a little disagreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not on death \Nrow! Get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been four and half days since they \Nleft the Maiden Island - Amazon Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Momonga! We \Nare arriving at Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and open the Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye-aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world's \Ngreatest prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were delayed a bit \Nbecause of head winds
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we have arrived \Nat Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy! We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Hancock now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock-dono! We are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! They have more navy ships \Nhere than when they did the Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most dangerous \Nplace in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so this is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But - you saw \Nthe Buster Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it only by \Nwhat I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an all-out attack by five vice \Nadmirals with a fleet of ten ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the strongest military \Noperation by the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where Ace is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he is being \Nheld deep underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get into my cloak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, \NVice Admiral Momonga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow! L-L-Look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the pirate empress! She's the \Nmost beautiful woman in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her beauty has no limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many volts is the power of \Nher beauty?! 10,000? 1,000,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that noise? \NIt hurts my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I turn them to stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy can't take \Nany more humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we already inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The condition \Nyou named was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see the key figure of this whole \Nmess, Portgaz D. Ace, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pirates are not welcomed here \Neven though you're a Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll put handcuffs made \Nof Sea Prism Stone on you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll conduct a strict \Nbody search before you go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we don't want any ploys \Nto free any of our prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, they'll \Nsearch my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll figure out a \Nway. Just go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Buggy the Clown \Nhas vanished from his cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ate a Devil Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Warden! Vice Admiral Momonga and \NHancock-dono of the Seven Warlords arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, c-c-cute! Open \Nthe gate please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it fully! Give her space!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock-sama! \NHave a nice visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mean! \NAnd take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dark atmosphere! \NThis must be hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, we got in! But \Nwe're not in the clear yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I got it wrong! I said \N"my" - jumping the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still the vice warden, \NHannyabal. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Momonga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're Empress \NHancock-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my Empress \NHancock-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm sorry! That \Nwas over-ambitious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dumb-ass-warden... \NOh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warden Magellan is in his office on \Nlevel 4 and I would like you to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Jail Manager Domino \Nand I will guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you are in a rush so \Nlet me ask you to come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral-dono, you can go that way. \NI'm afraid I have to conduct a body search.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were a prisoner, we'd ask you to go inside \Nof this cell and take off all of your clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we'd push you into an iron pot filled with \N"the warm water of hell" boiling at 200 degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to receive your baptism and get sterilized at \Nthe same time and you would be ready to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are different \Nclasses of prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among all recent \Nnewcomers, "Fire Fist" Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei of the Seven Warlords \Nand the former Warlord Crocodile
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't turn a hair while receiving baptism \Nand entered prison very smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in. We search guests \Nin a private room so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to take \Noff your cloak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are well-suited for hide \Nsomething inside so I'll take it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I don't trust you but you \Nbetter not do anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surveillance Transponder Snails are \Neverywhere inside of Impel Down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they keep sending video \Nto the surveillance monitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is the \Npirate empress!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's as beautiful \Nas they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snails! Let me see \NHancock-sama more clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close-up! Zoom \Nin for a close-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's just start.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me put these Sea Prism \NStone handcuffs on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a prisoner but \Nyou put handcuffs on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Public execution of Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is in 33 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy parts ways with Hancock and \Ninfiltrates the prison alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He slips through the guard \Nto search for Ace's floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he finds it harder than he \Nthought to penetrate Impel Down's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,iron-tight security.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, that man with \Nthe red nose appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Reunion in Hell?! The Man \NWho Ate the Chop-Chop Fruit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
